text="Theofanis Chatzidiamantis-Christoforidis">Theofanis Chatzidiamantis-Christoforidis</fr:title><fr:authors /></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>I am a first-year mathematics PhD student  at the University of Western Ontario, supervised by <fr:link
type="external"
href="https://jdc.math.uwo.ca/">Dan Christensen</fr:link>. I like (homotopy) type theory, (higher) category theory, and mathematical logic of all kinds.</fr:p><fr:p>I finished my master's at the University of Bonn in August 2024. I wrote <fr:link
type="external"
href="MscThesis.pdf">my thesis</fr:link> on simplicial type theory, supervised by <fr:link
type="external"
href="https://nimarasekh.github.io/">Nima Rasekh</fr:link> and <fr:link
type="external"
href="https://florisvandoorn.com/">Floris van Doorn</fr:link>. I contributed to the <fr:link
type="external"
href="https://github.com/rzk-lang/sHoTT">Rzk-sHoTT</fr:link> library of formal proofs, and started a little Rzk project of my own, working with 2-Segal types.</fr:p><fr:p>Before all that, I got my Bachelor's degree from the Aristotle University of Thessaloniki.</fr:p><fr:p><fr:link
type="external"
href="myself.jpg">Allowing for some degree of error, I look something like this.</fr:link></fr:p><fr:tree
