text="Current Projects">Current Projects</fr:title><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>10</fr:month><fr:day>11</fr:day></fr:date><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>31</fr:day></fr:date><fr:authors /></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p><fr:ul><fr:li>I am trying to formalise various forms of the <fr:em>bar induction</fr:em> axiom and their implications in Coq (in particular, the <fr:link
type="external"
href="https://github.com/HoTT/Coq-HoTT">Coq-HoTT</fr:link> library).</fr:li>
    <fr:li>[currently on hold] Together with <fr:link
type="external"
href="https://nimarasekh.github.io/">Nima Rasekh</fr:link>, we are wondering what we can prove about 2-Segal spaces synthetically, in the setting of simplicial type theory.</fr:li></fr:ul></fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree>
